# NAME: Ultra Mobile
# AUTHOR: KrisWei9527
# UPDATED: 2026-03-23
# 建议策略: 美国节点 (US Proxy)

# --- 核心官网与用户后台 ---
HOST-SUFFIX,ultramobile.com,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,my.ultramobile.com,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,shop.ultramobile.com,Proxy

# --- 激活与充值系统 ---
HOST-SUFFIX,activate.ultramobile.com,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,recharge.ultramobile.com,Proxy

# --- 底层通信与 API 服务 (重要：影响 App 登录) ---
HOST-SUFFIX,uvnv.com,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,mail.uvnv.com,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,api.uvnv.com,Proxy

# --- 关联支付与验证 (可选，若支付失败请务必包含) ---
HOST-KEYWORD,ultramobile,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,ultra.me,Proxy

# --- 常见第三方服务 (用于网页渲染和统计) ---
HOST-SUFFIX,cloudfront.net,Proxy

